  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.182686839479559         -4.9712          -114.64          -479.64
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.050143110185314          1.3645            31.47           131.65
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.028583694527874         -0.7778           -17.94           -75.05
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.123632243423965          3.3642            77.58           324.60
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

